    <summary>
      Fluent methods for asserting the result of TDD/BDD specs for Xamarin projects. Supports the unit test frameworks NUnit and NUnitLite.
    </summary>
    <description>
      A very extensive set of extension methods that allow you to more naturally specify the expected outcome of a TDD or 
      BDD-style unit test. This package adds Xamarin support. Supports the unit test frameworks NUnit PCL and NUnitLite.
    </description> 
